#Sana R.

#### Read about Sana and investigate the audit logs. Can you find any evidence of fraud?

**Your teacher** should provide you with an **activity guide** and **Sana's audit logs**. However, if you would like a digital version of the **activity guide, [click here](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1idByIUpqHOTgApWUPuuS4z4w3LHHP9zGh-Uo_VXbKGM/edit?usp=sharing)**. If you would like a digital version of **Sana's audit logs, [Click here](https://docs.google.com/document/d/1PWv-Ml0uWkXhHpiXJpRBscK_lFK4iOvAYeDboSVcG-M/edit?usp=sharing)**.


